{"type": "article", "id": 41218, "title": "音乐经典里的梗太多，他们做了个摇滚动物园｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-24T22:55:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 18808, "name": "Dorothy"}, {"id": 40778, "name": "Ocean Branding"}, {"id": 40779, "name": "SoFlow"}, {"id": 40780, "name": "Henri Judin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 155, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170524222339jZTpBbL1Jm9PFUft.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Rock ’N Roll Zoo by Dorothy</h3><p>还记得那个把歌名和地理结合在一起的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37525.html\">世界地图</a>吗？它背后的英国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.wearedorothy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dorothy</a> 擅长从音乐中挖掘有意思的细节。这条名为 Rock ’N Roll Zoo 的产品线就是他们以歌名或是乐团名中出现的动物为灵感设计，由艺术家 Tracy Worral 绘制而成的。在这个动物园内，你可以找到<a href=\"https://www.wearedorothy.com/collections/rock-n-roll-zoo/products/rock-n-roll-zoo-blackbird-special-edition\" rel=\"nofollow\">披头士的黑鸟</a>（Blackbird）、<a href=\"https://www.wearedorothy.com/collections/rock-n-roll-zoo/products/rock-n-roll-zoo-i-am-the-walrus\" rel=\"nofollow\">海象</a>（I am the Walrus）<a href=\"https://www.wearedorothy.com/collections/rock-n-roll-zoo/products/rock-n-roll-zoo-the-spiders-from-mars-12-print\" rel=\"nofollow\">大卫·鲍伊的火星蜘蛛</a>（The Spiders from Mars）等共计 77 只动物。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.wearedorothy.com/collections/rock-n-roll-zoo\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到包括马克杯、海报、T 恤和茶巾在内的商品，售价从 14 英镑起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222426aUuGA7wJn1prDI6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222426bganmWH89j6NLZJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222426teWwD2sQ9AVZOTYM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222426WlBGhkDnFu86fwm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lou by SoFlow</h3><p>来自瑞士的 <a href=\"http://so-flow.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SoFlow</a> 是一个致力于开发电动交通工具的设计公司，这款获得 2017 年红点设计奖的智能滑板 Lou 是旗下的第一款产品。和其他电动滑板不同的是，Lou 使用的马达和电池分别隐藏在可拆卸的电动轮和板面内，让滑板保持了原本的轻便和时尚感，同时还可以随时根据需要进行换装。用户可以通过配套的 App 设置运行模式或是接收损耗提示。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1985997854/meet-lou-the-real-electric-skateboard-shes-a-sure\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 299 瑞士法郎起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222459A8oDkpVqIeQj5vxH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222458daqCFvrfyzTtU0LV.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222458B4m0Sftnw1EqyDaA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.438750\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705242224581d8BV6IaJLg7FuXf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222502x083KwYAb4THJykE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Picklestone by Tanaka Tomonori</h3><p>现居日本京都的 <a href=\"http://hunter.kitchen/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tanaka Tomonori</a> 是一名广告从业人员，出于对料理的热爱，他还在本职工作以外参与了很多与食物有关的社团和企划。去年冬天，当他尝试腌制白菜时，发现市面上销售的塑料腌制盒不仅很容易占用冰箱空间，还很难让人与美观联系在一起。为此，他亲自设计了这款名为 Picklestone 的腌制工具，将矩形的盒子改成了圆柱形容器。加上由柏木和石头组成的配件，看起来要清爽许多，直接摆上餐桌也不会产生突兀感。目前 <a href=\"https://camp-fire.jp/projects/view/28916\" rel=\"nofollow\">Picklestone</a> 在日本众筹网站 Campfire 上的集资额已接近 500%，售价为 8000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017052422265245lmW8NrhvYUVxPJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666071\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222651nVp7mfe6Idwk14LR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222652Wfmaqhw5DYnxSKQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Parallel Universe Collection by Henri Judin</h3><p>以极简风格见长的芬兰设计师 <a href=\"http://henrijudin.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Henri Judin</a> 最近带来了一套名为 Parallel Universe 的家具，仅通过水平或是垂直方向的平行线营造出有趣的视觉效果。由于黑色的金属杆很容易让人联想到甘草糖，系列中成对设计的椅子和架子也因此被命名为 Liquorice；Sun &amp; Moon 指的是两张利用底部的交叉造成视觉错觉的桌子；规格完全相同的 Saturnus &amp; Uranus 这两款咖啡杯外部有着截然不同的起伏，同时也起到了保护手指不被烫伤的作用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705242227064xXJhtQoWCwM2ieV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222706VZgaXDwQAI5riKhl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705242227068CrI0TqJ469UmZvW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222707GuYOpI3ZmSzR6qQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924691\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222707NlajbRZevm69PEog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ombar by Ocean Branding</h3><p>英国有机巧克力品牌 <a href=\"https://www.ombar.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ombar</a> 最近委托创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.oceandesign.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ocean Branding</a> 为其重新设计了一套包装，以进一步强调“自然”的感觉。新包装上的文字采用了具有手写感的字体，正中央是一个像是用笔刷抹出的彩色字母 O，象征着品牌的首字母。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705242227270xdaiTRg7sLMCoWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222727cA6RCxYgohVwdHnm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.840000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222729FpfJ7GKR5OVqiA3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.840000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Débarrassons le Plancher by Byme Architecture</h3><p class=\"\">为了还原出古迹的原貌，帮助人们更好地了解历史，来自法国 <a href=\"http://www.byme-architecture.com/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Byme</a> 建筑事务所的 Fanny Bouchet 和 Emmanuelle Messier 在艾格莫尔特（Aigues-Mortes）的一座堡垒里创作了一个意为“让我们摆脱地板”（Débarrassons le Plancher）的艺术装置。他们的灵感来源于旧时用来欺骗入侵者的陷阱，整个装置由三千多块手工切割的木块构成，直接覆盖了本身的地面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705242227434GVcuS5I6NF0HT8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222742Tr8yphCu9xcbeIY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222743bPoVYO8UZipkxWwv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170524222742ZdrGgDYu9yLHi63F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.404615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}